BYO formatting task tracking plugin

Adds the following commands:

`:Focus` - enables the other commands - use this if you aren't using `.todo` file extension

The following commands are automatically registered if you open a file
with a `.todo` file extension

`:FNO` - find next on-deck
`:FNN` - find next doing-now
`:FNX` - find next done

Assumes the following task annotations:

	[ ] a task that is not done
	[c] a task currently in progress
	[n] also a task currently in progress
	[x] a task that's done
